SCABA Spring Contest (Championship Section) 0 Own Choice Test Piece Contest SCABA Spring Contest scaba-spring-contest
Town Hall, Hove, Sussex British Bandsman 4/6/1960 advertises this contest and Daily Herald Brighton contest to be held on same day. Dartford also gained 3rd prize in section 2 at the Brighton Contest. Locations only about 2 miles apart. March contest - 1st Croydon, 2nd Dartford, 3rd City of Cambridge.
